title: Episode 164: She's downstairs!? (Feat. Zoey Dollaz)
itunes:title: Episode 164: She's downstairs!? (Feat. Zoey Dollaz)
description:
Rapper Zoey Dollaz joins the ladies of Lip Service this week and opens up about his emotional side. He speaks on his his past and current relationships, his dreams of being a pilot, his intolerance for domestic abuse, and much more! Zoey Dollaz even details his experience with role-playing in the bedroom. Enjoy!
